            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.5.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.1</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## What's New in 2.5.2

### 2.5.3 Fixes
Removed app data permissions needed for the desktop widgets.

## 2.5.2 Changes

### Retro Theme
New skeuomorphic Retro theme with beveled day cells, bezel card frame, vintage header bar, and burnt-orange event dots. Dark-mode detection wired through the widget background.

### Widget Enhancements
Reworked widget calendar grid with App Intents support and configurable customization. Tithi now shows conditionally based on settings, and theme gradient colors sync from the app to the widget.

### Settings & Polish
Refined settings window and menu, retro-style header nav buttons and event tabs, and assorted theme fixes.
]]></description>
